msgstr "Rather, it has only reached the bark.”"

#. </p><h3>
msgctxt "dn25:59.1"
msgid "2.4. Parisuddhaphegguppattakathā"
msgstr "On Reaching the Softwood"

#. </h3><p><a class="sc" id="52"></a><a class="wp" id="wp18"></a>
#. VAR: pana → ca kho pana (bj) | kho pana (c1)
msgctxt "dn25:60.1"
msgid "“Kittāvatā pana, bhante, tapojigucchā aggappattā ca hoti sārappattā ca?"
msgstr ""
"“But at what point, sir, does the mortification in disgust of sin reach the "
"peak and the pith?"

msgctxt "dn25:60.2"
msgid ""
"Sādhu me, bhante, bhagavā tapojigucchāya aggaññeva pāpetu, sāraññeva "
"pāpetū”ti."
msgstr "Please help me reach the peak and the pith!”"

