msgctxt "dn25:61.2"
msgid "Kathañca, nigrodha, tapassī cātuyāmasaṃvarasaṃvuto hoti …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn25:61.3"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn25:61.4"
msgid ""
"yato kho, nigrodha, tapassī cātuyāmasaṃvarasaṃvuto hoti, aduṃ cassa hoti "
"tapassitāya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn25:61.5"
msgid "So abhiharati no hīnāyāvattati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn25:61.6"
msgid "So vivittaṃ senāsanaṃ bhajati …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn25:61.7"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn25:61.8"
msgid ""
"so ime pañca nīvaraṇe pahāya cetaso upakkilese paññāya dubbalīkaraṇe "
"mettāsahagatena cetasā …"
msgstr ""
"They give up these five hindrances, corruptions of the heart that weaken "
"wisdom. Then they meditate spreading a heart full of love …"

msgctxt "dn25:61.9"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn25:61.10"
msgid "karuṇāsahagatena cetasā …"
msgstr "compassion …"

msgctxt "dn25:61.11"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn25:61.12"
msgid "muditāsahagatena cetasā …"
msgstr "rejoicing …"

msgctxt "dn25:61.13"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn25:61.14"
msgid ""
"upekkhāsahagatena cetasā vipulena mahaggatena appamāṇena averena abyāpajjena "
"pharitvā viharati."
msgstr "equanimity."

msgctxt "dn25:61.15"
msgid "So anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ anussarati seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr "They recollect many kinds of past lives, that is,"

msgctxt "dn25:61.16"
msgid ""
"ekampi jātiṃ dvepi jātiyo tissopi jātiyo catassopi jātiyo pañcapi jātiyo "
"dasapi jātiyo vīsampi jātiyo tiṃsampi jātiyo cattālīsampi jātiyo paññāsampi "
"jātiyo jātisatampi jātisahassampi jātisatasahassampi anekepi saṃvaṭṭakappe "
"anekepi vivaṭṭakappe anekepi saṃvaṭṭavivaṭṭakappe:"
msgstr ""
"one, two, three, four, five, ten, twenty, thirty, forty, fifty, a hundred, a "
"thousand, a hundred thousand lives; many eons of the world contracting, many "
"eons of the world evolving, many eons of the world contracting and evolving. "
"They remember: "

msgctxt "dn25:61.17"
msgid ""
"‘amutrāsiṃ evaṃnāmo evaṃgotto evaṃvaṇṇo evamāhāro "
"evaṃsukhadukkhappaṭisaṃvedī evamāyupariyanto, so tato cuto amutra udapādiṃ, "
"tatrāpāsiṃ evaṃnāmo evaṃgotto evaṃvaṇṇo evamāhāro "
"evaṃsukhadukkhappaṭisaṃvedī evamāyupariyanto, so tato cuto idhūpapanno’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘There, I was named this, my clan was that, I looked like this, and that was "
"my food. This was how I felt pleasure and pain, and that was how my life "
"ended. When I passed away from that place I was reborn somewhere else. "
"There, too, I was named this, my clan was that, I looked like this, and that "
"was my food. This was how I felt pleasure and pain, and that was how my life "
"ended. When I passed away from that place I was reborn here.’"

msgctxt "dn25:61.18"
msgid "Iti sākāraṃ sauddesaṃ anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ anussarati."
msgstr ""
"And so they recollect their many kinds of past lives, with features and "
"details. "

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="54"></a>
