"brahmacariyapariyosānaṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā "
"upasampajja viharissati sattāhaṃ’."
msgstr ""

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "dn25:77.1"
msgid "6. Paribbājakānaṃpajjhāyana"
msgstr "The Wanderers Feel Depressed"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="66"></a><a class="wp" id="wp23"></a>
#. VAR: pana te → panetaṃ (c1)
msgctxt "dn25:78.1"
msgid "Siyā kho pana te, nigrodha, evamassa:"
msgstr "Nigrodha, you might think: "

msgctxt "dn25:78.2"
msgid "‘antevāsikamyatā no samaṇo gotamo evamāhā’ti."
msgstr "‘The ascetic Gotama speaks like this because he wants pupils.’"

msgctxt "dn25:78.3"
msgid "Na kho panetaṃ, nigrodha, evaṃ daṭṭhabbaṃ."
msgstr "But you should not see it like this."

#. VAR: vo → te (bj)
msgctxt "dn25:78.4"
msgid "Yo eva vo ācariyo, so eva vo ācariyo hotu."
msgstr "Let your teacher remain your teacher."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="67"></a>
msgctxt "dn25:79.1"
msgid "Siyā kho pana te, nigrodha, evamassa:"
msgstr "You might think: "

msgctxt "dn25:79.2"
msgid "‘uddesā no cāvetukāmo samaṇo gotamo evamāhā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘The ascetic Gotama speaks like this because he wants us to give up our "
"recitation.’"

msgctxt "dn25:79.3"
msgid "Na kho panetaṃ, nigrodha, evaṃ daṭṭhabbaṃ."
msgstr "But you should not see it like this."

msgctxt "dn25:79.4"
msgid "Yo eva vo uddeso so eva vo uddeso hotu."
msgstr "Let your recitation remain as it is."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="68"></a>
msgctxt "dn25:80.1"
msgid "Siyā kho pana te, nigrodha, evamassa:"
msgstr "You might think: "

msgctxt "dn25:80.2"
msgid "‘ājīvā no cāvetukāmo samaṇo gotamo evamāhā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘The ascetic Gotama speaks like this because he wants us to give up our "
"livelihood.’"

msgctxt "dn25:80.3"
msgid "Na kho panetaṃ, nigrodha, evaṃ daṭṭhabbaṃ."
msgstr "But you should not see it like this."

msgctxt "dn25:80.4"
msgid "Yo eva vo ājīvo, so eva vo ājīvo hotu."
msgstr "Let your livelihood remain as it is."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="69"></a>
msgctxt "dn25:81.1"
msgid "Siyā kho pana te, nigrodha, evamassa:"
msgstr "You might think: "

msgctxt "dn25:81.2"
msgid ""
"‘ye no dhammā akusalā akusalasaṅkhātā sācariyakānaṃ, tesu patiṭṭhāpetukāmo "
"samaṇo gotamo evamāhā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘The ascetic Gotama speaks like this because he wants us to start doing "
"things that are unskillful and considered unskillful in our tradition.’"

msgctxt "dn25:81.3"
msgid "Na kho panetaṃ, nigrodha, evaṃ daṭṭhabbaṃ."
msgstr "But you should not see it like this."

#. VAR: ceva vo te dhammā → vo dhammā (bj, mr) | te dhammā (s1-3)
msgctxt "dn25:81.4"
msgid "Akusalā ceva vo te dhammā hontu akusalasaṅkhātā ca sācariyakānaṃ."
msgstr ""
"Let those things that are unskillful and considered unskillful in your "
"tradition remain as they are."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="70"></a>
msgctxt "dn25:82.1"
msgid "Siyā kho pana te, nigrodha, evamassa:"
msgstr "You might think: "

msgctxt "dn25:82.2"
msgid ""
"‘ye no dhammā kusalā kusalasaṅkhātā sācariyakānaṃ, tehi vivecetukāmo samaṇo "
"gotamo evamāhā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘The ascetic Gotama speaks like this because he wants us to stop doing "
"things that are skillful and considered skillful in our tradition.’"

msgctxt "dn25:82.3"
msgid "Na kho panetaṃ, nigrodha, evaṃ daṭṭhabbaṃ."
msgstr "But you should not see it like this."

msgctxt "dn25:82.4"
msgid "Kusalā ceva vo te dhammā hontu kusalasaṅkhātā ca sācariyakānaṃ."
msgstr ""
"Let those things that are skillful and considered skillful in your tradition "
"remain as they are."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="71"></a><a class="pts" id="pts3.57"></a>
#. VAR: napi ājīvā cāvetukāmo evaṃ vadāmi, napi ye vo dhammā → napi ye ca kho
#. dhammā (bj) | napi ye te dhammā (s1-3) | napi ye ca vo dhammā (mr)
#. VAR: napi ye vo dhammā → napi ye ca kho dhammā (bj) | napi ye te dhammā
#. (s1-3) | napi ye ca vo dhammā (mr)
msgctxt "dn25:83.1"
msgid ""
"Iti khvāhaṃ, nigrodha, neva antevāsikamyatā evaṃ vadāmi, napi uddesā "
"cāvetukāmo evaṃ vadāmi, napi ājīvā cāvetukāmo evaṃ vadāmi, napi ye vo dhammā "
"akusalā akusalasaṅkhātā sācariyakānaṃ, tesu patiṭṭhāpetukāmo evaṃ vadāmi, "
"napi ye vo dhammā kusalā kusalasaṅkhātā sācariyakānaṃ, tehi vivecetukāmo "
"evaṃ vadāmi."
msgstr "I do not speak for any of these reasons."

#. VAR: sadarā → sadarathā (s1-3, mr) | saddarā (pts1, mr)
#. VAR: ponobbhavikā → ponobhavikā (bj, pts1, mr)
msgctxt "dn25:83.2"
msgid ""
"Santi ca kho, nigrodha, akusalā dhammā appahīnā saṃkilesikā ponobbhavikā "
"sadarā dukkhavipākā āyatiṃ jātijarāmaraṇiyā, yesāhaṃ pahānāya dhammaṃ desemi."
msgstr ""
"Nigrodha, there are things that are unskillful, corrupted, leading to future "
"lives, hurtful, resulting in suffering and future birth, old age, and death. "
"I teach Dhamma so that those things may be given up."

msgctxt "dn25:83.3"
msgid ""
"Yathāpaṭipannānaṃ vo saṃkilesikā dhammā pahīyissanti, vodānīyā dhammā "
"abhivaḍḍhissanti, paññāpāripūriṃ vepullattañca diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā "
"sacchikatvā upasampajja viharissathā”ti."
msgstr ""
"When you practice accordingly, corrupting qualities will be given up in you "
"and cleansing qualities will grow. You’ll enter and remain in the fullness "
"and abundance of wisdom, having realized it with your own insight in this "
"very life.”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="72"></a><a class="wp" id="wp24"></a>
msgctxt "dn25:84.1"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ vutte, te paribbājakā tuṇhībhūtā maṅkubhūtā pattakkhandhā adhomukhā "
"pajjhāyantā appaṭibhānā nisīdiṃsu yathā taṃ mārena pariyuṭṭhitacittā."
msgstr ""
"When this was said, those wanderers sat silent, dismayed, shoulders "
"drooping, downcast, depressed, with nothing to say, as if their minds were "
"possessed by Māra."

msgctxt "dn25:84.2"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavato etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then the Buddha thought:"

msgctxt "dn25:84.3"
msgid "“sabbepime moghapurisā phuṭṭhā pāpimatā."
msgstr "“All these foolish people have been touched by the Wicked One!"

msgctxt "dn25:84.4"
msgid "Yatra hi nāma ekassapi na evaṃ bhavissati:"
msgstr "For not even a single one thinks:"

msgctxt "dn25:84.5"
msgid ""
"‘handa mayaṃ aññāṇatthampi samaṇe gotame brahmacariyaṃ carāma, kiṃ karissati "
"sattāho’”ti?"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="73"></a>
#. VAR: paccupaṭṭhāsi → paccuṭṭhāsi (bj, s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "dn25:85.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bhagavā udumbarikāya paribbājakārāme sīhanādaṃ naditvā vehāsaṃ "
"abbhuggantvā gijjhakūṭe pabbate paccupaṭṭhāsi."
msgstr ""
"Then the Buddha, having roared his lion’s roar in the lady Udumbarikā’s "
"monastery for wanderers, rose into the air and landed on Vulture’s Peak."

msgctxt "dn25:85.2"
msgid "Sandhāno pana gahapati tāvadeva rājagahaṃ pāvisīti."
msgstr "Meanwhile, the householder Sandhāna just went back to Rājagaha."

#. </p><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "dn25:86.1"
msgid "Udumbarikasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
